reviewText: It's okay.  None of the methods they use in this video worked for us or our birds.  Also, there was nothing but voice over and words on the screen, which is about as boring as you can get.  It would have been a far better buy had there been video of them working with consultation birds or other birds with problems.  I wouldn't buy anything else from them, personally.  It's all perfect world advice for people who have nothing else in their lives but their birds.  It's not for the real world.

Excellent training video.  Easy to follow and implement. My two conures had better behavior after one week of training with the Womach techniques.
